<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.10">
<l>viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāṉī vēṇṭāyē yāyiṭiṉum</l>
<l>maṟṟārum paṟṟillē ṉeṉṟavaṉait tāḷnayanta</l>
<l>koṟṟavēṟ ṟāṉaik kulacē karaṉcoṉṉa</l>
<l>naṟṟamiḻppat tumvallār naṇṇār narakamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master all ten [poems] in good Tamil,</l>
<l rend="indent">uttered by Kulacēkaraṉ with a victorious spear [and] army,</l>
<l rend="indent">who longed for His feet saying, ‘I do not have anyone else [as my] support</l>
<l rend="indent">even though You do not want [me], O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu,’</l>
<l>shall not reach hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
